  <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary">About MyBasecamp2</h2>
  <br>
  <p>
    Welcome to <strong>MyBasecamp2</strong>, the next evolution of MyBasecamp1! This version enhances project collaboration by introducing 
    <strong>attachments, discussion threads, and messaging</strong>, making teamwork more efficient.
  </p>

  <h3 class="fw-bold">New Features in MyBasecamp2</h3>
  <p>Building on the foundations of MyBasecamp1, MyBasecamp2 introduces:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Attachments:</strong> Upload and manage PNG, JPG, PDF, and TXT files inside a project.</li>
    <li><strong>Discussion Threads:</strong> Admins can create and manage discussion threads.</li>
    <li><strong>Messaging:</strong> Users can post, edit, and delete messages inside threads.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="fw-bold">Why MyBasecamp2?</h3>
  <p>Our platform makes collaboration seamless by allowing users to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>✅ <strong>Sign up & manage accounts</strong></li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Log in & log out securely</strong></li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Create and manage projects</strong></li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Upload and manage project files</strong></li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Engage in discussions with team members</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="fw-bold">Project Roadmap</h3>
  <p>MyBasecamp2 is being developed in structured phases:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Phase 1:</strong> User Authentication – Register, log in, and manage user roles.</li>
    <li><strong>Phase 2:</strong> Project & File Management – Create, edit, delete projects, and upload attachments.</li>
    <li><strong>Phase 3:</strong> Enhanced Collaboration – Add discussion threads, messaging, and cloud deployment.</li>
  </ul>

